  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Draw Your Own Solutions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels aren’t just obstacles: they’re sketches waiting to be completed. <br>Create platforms, bounce pads, and shortcuts on the fly to solve puzzles your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.poster.avif?t=1773695369\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.webm?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.mp4?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore 5 Worlds + a Finale Zone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world has its own theme, hazards, secrets, and boss.<br>Play through verdant forests, frozen peaks, sunny beaches, treacherous deserts, and more. Then, face the abstract finale where everything breaks the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/18ad2ba0f7ce740d07fd721779d6d9c6.avif?t=1773695369\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras_big/18ad2ba0f7ce740d07fd721779d6d9c6.webp?t=1773695369 width=1560 height=880 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock 60+ Costumes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dress Bob and Liz in everything from space suits to formalwear to crossover outfits from other Wayward Thoughts games. Costumes are earned through exploration, secrets, tokens, or luck in Ferdinand’s shop. No microtransactions. No paid DLC. Period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3f27c0e7ee24e27d3fb1f4023c4c0a8f.poster.avif?t=1773695369\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3f27c0e7ee24e27d3fb1f4023c4c0a8f.webm?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3f27c0e7ee24e27d3fb1f4023c4c0a8f.mp4?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Your Way with Modifiers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're here for the challenge or just the vibes, Super Sketch Bob adapts to <i>you</i>. Slow the game down, turn off spiders (ew!), or activate infinite health. It’s your sketchbook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/0d97569c24e94a64e25c61215a6390e2.avif?t=1773695369\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras_big/0d97569c24e94a64e25c61215a6390e2.webp?t=1773695369 width=1560 height=761 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Secrets of the Sketchbook</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden rooms, alternate exits, collectible tokens, and mysteries reward curious players.  You can finish the story without 100% or dive deep and find everything!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Tale of Two Siblings </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bob creates. Liz erases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When she starts wiping out the world with a magic eraser, Bob grabs the only thing that can undo the damage: a pencil powerful enough to redraw reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story starts simple, but the heart is real: a brother, a sister, and a whole sketchbook full of surprising moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.poster.avif?t=1773695369\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.webm?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.mp4?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bonus: Cross/Link Support</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/958d00e83c32835ee7b0ada54b47e3f7.avif?t=1773695369\" width=220 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Owning other Wayward Thoughts games unlocks extra costumes automatically once you've found secret items in each game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently compatible with <strong>Logical Labyrinth DX</strong>, with future titles expanding the system. See our website for details: </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Draw Your Own Solutions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels aren’t just obstacles: they’re sketches waiting to be completed. <br>Create platforms, bounce pads, and shortcuts on the fly to solve puzzles your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.poster.avif?t=1773695369\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.webm?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/3cf7242b8da6fad5594d3ad10ae6357f.mp4?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore 5 Worlds + a Finale Zone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each world has its own theme, hazards, secrets, and boss.<br>Play through verdant forests, frozen peaks, sunny beaches, treacherous deserts, and more. Then, face the abstract finale where everything breaks the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/18ad2ba0f7ce740d07fd721779d6d9c6.avif?t=1773695369\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras_big/18ad2ba0f7ce740d07fd721779d6d9c6.webp?t=1773695369 width=1560 height=880 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock 60+ Costumes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dress Bob and Liz in everything from space suits to formalwear to crossover outfits from other Wayward Thoughts games. Costumes are earned through exploration, secrets, tokens, or luck in Ferdinand’s shop. No microtransactions. No paid DLC. Period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video