"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.poster.avif?t=1773695369\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.webm?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/a724d3eb7ec644b681221a9b5aa0550f.mp4?t=1773695369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bonus: Cross/Link Support</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/497870/extras/958d00e83c32835ee7b0ada54b47e3f7.avif?t=1773695369\" width=220 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Owning other Wayward Thoughts games unlocks extra costumes automatically once you've found secret items in each game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently compatible with <strong>Logical Labyrinth DX</strong>, with future titles expanding the system. See our website for details: </p>",
